text: "Key West Intermezzo (I Saw You First)" is a 1996 song by John Mellencamp and taken from his 14th studio album Mr. Happy Go Lucky. It went to number 1 in Canada, number 14 in the United States and charted for the last time in Australia and New Zealand. == References == Category:1996 songs Category:John Mellencamp songs
title: Key West Intermezzo (I Saw You First)
